# Docket_stage + Docket_complete are TRACKED (Battlewrath): transient in INTENT (consumed/cleared as they process),
# but a big staged batch and its OUTPUTS must SURVIVE git - we don't want to regenerate 1000s of files just because
# they weren't committed. Commit them via the normal push when a batch is worth keeping.
#
# receipts/ stays ignored - verbose per-run execution logs, genuinely disposable. The survivable run-log is the
# compact Docket_complete/register.jsonl (one line per pack), which rides along with Docket_complete.
receipts/
